{"tid":1211544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廣傳 如果你唔係好舒服","createTime":"2019-06-12T15:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T16:02:41.000Z","uid":237145,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"843b02f4ca51b1ffb4d54505444ba75f0b2a45d2","tid":1211544,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"記住<br />\n唔舒服嘅時候要冷靜<br />\n急症室睇醫生<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔記得咗帶身分證完全唔緊要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為醫院會照睇你<br />\n<br />\n講清楚係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊度唔舒服</span></span> 因為你講乜醫護就會寫乜 完全信你㗎<br />\n<br />\n如果咁唔好彩有事故勞煩到班公安 例如車禍<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係有得你揀畀唔畀驗身報告公安</span>[/size=4]</span><br />\n<br />\n想嘅咪畀囉<br />\n冇人迫到你㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝大家身體健康！"},{"pid":"7ec31bdfee24dddacf07e1bef907ead4617ba1c6","tid":1211544,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T16:02:41.000Z","msg":"推"}]}